{
  "page": "Wedding of Roose Bolton and Walda Frey",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png/350px-Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"287\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png/525px-Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png/700px-Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Fat_walda_and_her_hubby_by_jubah.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>, by Juliana Pinho ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>wedding of Roose Bolton and Walda Frey</b> takes place in <a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a> marries <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Frey</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Wedding\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Wedding</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Attendees\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Attendees</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Roose_Bolton_and_Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Dreadfort\" title=\"Lord of the Dreadfort\">Lord of the Dreadfort</a>, retreats to the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> after being defeated by <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Lord of Casterly Rock\">Lord of Casterly Rock</a>, at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">battle on the Green Fork</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Roose, twice a widower,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> agrees to marry a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Crossing\" title=\"Lord of the Crossing\">Lord of the Crossing</a>, offers the bride's weight in <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> for a dowry, so Roose chooses Walder's fifteen-year-old granddaughter <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda</a>, who is known as \"Fat Walda\" because of her weight.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wedding\">Wedding</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Roose_Bolton_and_Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Wedding\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Roose and Walda marry at the Twins.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Walda is pleased that she is chosen instead of her slimmer cousin, <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Walton)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Walton)\">Fair Walda</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> The bride's father, <a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Merrett Frey</a>, hopes that his fortunes will rise through the Bolton-Frey alliance, but Lord Walder mocks his son over Walda's weight.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Roose_Bolton_and_Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After Tywin retreats to <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>, Roose takes the <a href=\"/index.php/Ruby_ford\" title=\"Ruby ford\">ruby ford</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Crossroads\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crossroads\">crossroads</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> When Tywin marches west to confront <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> sends word for Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Helman_Tallhart\" title=\"Helman Tallhart\">Helman Tallhart</a> to depart the Twins and join Roose in a <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Fall of Harrenhal\">campaign against Harrenhal</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Walda sends frequent letters from the Twins to Roose while he is encamped at Harrenhal.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Roose hopes to have a trueborn son with Walda,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> as he fears his <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> son, <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Snow</a>, murdered his heir, <a href=\"/index.php/Domeric_Bolton\" title=\"Domeric Bolton\">Domeric Bolton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the aftermath of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> names Roose as <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a> and legitimizes Ramsay.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> While at <a href=\"/index.php/Barrowton\" title=\"Barrowton\">Barrowton</a>, Roose informs the captive <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> that he has become fond of Walda, though he expects that Ramsay will kill any sons she births.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> At <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, Theon notices that Walda is pregnant.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Roose_Bolton_and_Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I pray for you morn, noon, and night, my sweet lord, and count the days until you share my bed again. Return to me soon, and I will give you many trueborn sons to take the place of your dear <a href=\"/index.php/Domeric_Bolton\" title=\"Domeric Bolton\">Domeric</a> and rule the <a href=\"/index.php/Dreadfort\" title=\"Dreadfort\">Dreadfort</a> after you.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Frey</a> writing to <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Roose</b>: I wed the Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Frey</a> whilst I was at the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a>.<br />\n</p><p><b>Jaime</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Walton)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Walton)\">Fair Walda</a>?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Roose</b>: Fat Walda. My <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">lord of Frey</a> offered me my bride's weight in <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> for a dowry, so I chose accordingly.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Everyone thought my lord would choose <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Walton)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Walton)\">Fair Walda</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">My lord grandfather</a> offered <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose</a> his bride's weight in <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> as a dowry, though, so my lord of Bolton picked me. I weigh six stone more than Fair Walda, but that was the first time I was glad of it. I'm Lady Bolton now and my cousin's still a <a href=\"/index.php/Maid\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maid\">maid</a>, and she'll be nineteen soon, poor thing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Frey</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Wendel_Manderly\" title=\"Wendel Manderly\">Wendel Manderly</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>He picked her because she's fat. You think <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Bolton</a> gave a <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">mummer</a>'s fart that she was your whelp? Think he sat about thinking, 'Heh, Merrett Muttonhead, that's the very man I need for a good-father'? Your <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda's</a> a sow in <a href=\"/index.php/Silk\" title=\"Silk\">silk</a>, that's why he picked her, and I'm not like to thank you for it. We'd have had the same alliance at half the price if your little porkling put down her spoon from time to time.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Merrett Frey</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Attendees\">Attendees</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Roose_Bolton_and_Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Attendees\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\"><img alt=\"House Bolton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/20px-House_Bolton.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/30px-House_Bolton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/40px-House_Bolton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/20px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/30px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/40px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/20px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/30px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/40px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Erenford\" title=\"House Erenford\"><img alt=\"House Erenford.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/House_Erenford.svg/20px-House_Erenford.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/House_Erenford.svg/30px-House_Erenford.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c0/House_Erenford.svg/40px-House_Erenford.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Joyeuse_Erenford\" title=\"Joyeuse Erenford\">Joyeuse Erenford</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/20px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/30px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/40px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Merrett Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tallhart\" title=\"House Tallhart\"><img alt=\"House Tallhart.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Tallhart.svg/20px-H